  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5444396/" class="title-link">蒼狼與白鹿的內亂和擴張</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5444396"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/51301914/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u51301914-5.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/51301914/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">咸咖啡</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-05-27"
      class="main-meta">2012-05-27 23:31:19</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5444396_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  其實我看的是《蒙古帝國－蒼狼與白鹿》，作者是劉學銚。  本書基本把蒙古帝國的前前後後，左左右右都交代了。但還是不夠深入，一種宏觀的敘事方式，就會缺乏一些深度。但作者顯然是研究蒙古的專家，只是篇幅所限不能暢言。並且此書弄成初級閱讀版的樣式，讀起來很不暢快。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
